Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: "I don't know how to work with a commandant like you.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Huh?', 3: '5', 4: 'What were the commandants you worked with like?', 5: '6'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "I'm sorry. That came out of nowhere.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Having a stronger sense of rank and station, keeping the relationship between superiors and subordinates professional. The kind Karenina despises.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'But I believe that respecting the hierarchy of our station is also instrumental to our success.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'To put it simply, I hope that you would treat us more like tools in the future, Commandant.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "Of course, you're free to treat the Gray Ravens how you have always treated them. But as for me...", 4: '1'}
{2: "You're part of Gray Raven now.", 3: '11', 4: "Doesn't it make you uncomfortable to be treated as a tool?", 5: '12'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'More like a liaison than a member, I would say. I still belong to the Purifying Force on the system files.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "I will handle my feelings. You don't have to worry about that.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Your recent showings of intimacy, like the gifts you offered me, have caught me off guard.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "I don't think I can reciprocate the way you were hoping for like how Liv or Nanami could.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "So I'd advise you against spending time on me.", 4: '1'}
